text: Interstate 516 (I-516), also known as the W.F. Lynes Parkway, is a auxiliary Interstate Highway in Savannah, Georgia. It starts at Georgia State Route 21 (SR 21) in Garden City, and ends at the same road (SR 21) in Savannah. It meets with I-16 also in Savannah. ==References== Category:Interstate Highways
title: Interstate 516
